snippet.title: Walk Home: Videogame Trailer
snippet.description:
hi hello, this is the trailer for my upcomming videogame "Walk home"

this is my second solo project, and im excited to see what people think of it.

In this game you simply walk home after a visit to your significant other was cut short, with a feeling that something is off...

This is an exploration-based game where your detective skills we be rewarded.



it will be up on my itch.io page: https://hengikken.itch.io/
